import { Component, Input, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-content', templateUrl: './content.component.html', styleUrls: ['./content.component.css'], }) export class ContentComponent implements OnInit { @Input() title: string; employeeList: any = []; private LOGO = require("./assets/images/2.jpg"); constructor(private http : HttpClient) { this.title = ''; } ngOnInit(): void { this.getItem(); } getItem() { this.http.get('http://localhost:9000/employee').subscribe(data=>{ this.employeeList = data; }) } }
